videos.headline: Kent State running back goes full video game mode, breaks five tackles
videos.description: Kent State's Justin Rankin catchs the ball over the middle and then jukes out one defender, adds in a pair of nasty spin moves and then busts through a few more tackles before finally being brought down for a 54-yard gain.
